World Cup 2018-2022: FIFA designates the organizing countries
Amid the storm of corruption suspicions, FIFA’s executive committee on Thursday designated the countries hosting the 2018 and 2022 World Cups, a clear political choice where influence struggles and lobbying may come to take precedence over technical criteria.
